---
// src/pages/affiliate-disclosure.astro
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
const updated = "June 2025";
---

<style>
  .legal-hero { background: var(--grad-hero); padding: 3.5rem 0 3rem; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .legal-hero h1 { font-size: clamp(1.75rem, 4vw, 2.5rem); margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-meta  { font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: 0.5rem; }
  .legal-body  { max-width: 780px; margin-inline: auto; padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 5rem; }
  .legal-body h2 { font-size: 1.2rem; margin: 2.5rem 0 0.75rem; padding-top: 2rem; border-top: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .legal-body h2:first-of-type { border-top: none; margin-top: 0; }
  .legal-body p  { margin-bottom: 1rem; line-height: 1.8; font-size: 0.97rem; }
  .legal-body ul { list-style: disc; padding-left: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 1rem; }
  .legal-body ul li { margin-bottom: 0.4rem; line-height: 1.7; font-size: 0.95rem; }
  .legal-body a  { color: var(--coral); }
  .highlight-box {
    background: #FFF8F4;
    border: 2px solid var(--coral);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--text-body);
  }
  .highlight-box strong { color: var(--text-dark); }
</style>

<BaseLayout
  title="Affiliate Disclosure — Smart Reward Finds"
  description="Smart Reward Finds Affiliate Disclosure — how we handle affiliate and partner links on this site."
>
  <section class="legal-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <span class="section-label">Legal</span>
      <h1>Affiliate Disclosure</h1>
      <p class="legal-meta">Last updated: {updated}</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="legal-body container">

    <div class="highlight-box">
      <strong>Short version:</strong> Some links on Smart Reward Finds are affiliate or partner links.
      If you click one and take an action (like signing up or making a purchase), we may earn a small commission —
      at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the site running. It never changes what we recommend.
    </div>

    <h2>What Is an Affiliate Link?</h2>
    <p>
      An affiliate link is a special URL that contains a unique tracking code. When you click an affiliate link
      and complete a qualifying action — such as signing up for a platform, making a purchase, or completing an
      offer — the company that runs that platform pays Smart Reward Finds a small referral fee or commission.
    </p>
    <p>
      You don't pay anything extra by using an affiliate link. The commission comes from the company's marketing
      budget, not from you.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Handle Affiliate Relationships</h2>
    <p>
      Smart Reward Finds may contain affiliate links to third-party products, services, platforms, tools,
      reward apps, and offers. These relationships may influence which content we choose to write about,
      but they do not influence our editorial honesty or our obligation to share useful, accurate information.
    </p>
    <p>We follow these principles in our affiliate relationships:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>We only share affiliates and offers we genuinely believe are worth mentioning.</li>
      <li>We clearly disclose when a link may be an affiliate link, either in individual posts or through site-wide notices like this page.</li>
      <li>We do not inflate claims about offers to generate more clicks.</li>
      <li>We try to keep content updated when offer terms change, though we cannot always do so immediately.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>FTC Disclosure Compliance</h2>
    <p>
      In accordance with the Federal Trade Commission's (FTC) guidelines concerning the use of endorsements and
      testimonials in advertising (16 CFR Part 255), Smart Reward Finds discloses that some links on this site
      may be affiliate or partner links. This disclosure applies to all content published on this website.
    </p>
    <p>
      When a post contains affiliate links, you may see a disclosure note within the post itself as well.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-Party Products &amp; Services</h2>
    <p>
      Smart Reward Finds does not own or operate the products, services, apps, or platforms it writes about.
      Any opinions expressed are our own. We are not responsible for the accuracy of third-party offers,
      for changes to third-party terms, or for the results you experience using any third-party product or service.
    </p>
    <p>
      Always do your own research and read the official terms of any offer, platform, or service before
      participating. Third-party terms can change without notice.
    </p>

    <h2>Questions?</h2>
    <p>
      If you have questions about our affiliate relationships or specific links on this site,
      please <a href="/contact">contact us</a>.
    </p>

  </div>
</BaseLayout>
